{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8948", "repo": "rails", "body": "As of now (thanks, steveklabnik!) the official 2.3 branch has gemspecs. So you can add this to your gemfile to pick up Ernie's fix for CVE-2013-0155:\r\n\r\n````ruby\r\ngit 'git://github.com/rails/rails.git', :branch => '2-3-stable' do\r\n  gem 'rails'\r\n  gem 'actionmailer'\r\n  gem 'actionpack'\r\n  gem 'activerecord'\r\n  gem 'activeresource'\r\n  gem 'activesupport'\r\nend\r\n````\r\n\r\nAfter doing that, if there are additional commits to the branch in the future, run `bundle update rails` to pick them up.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ee64bd3543c151009f81"}, "issue_id": 8948, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/12573404", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8948#issuecomment-12573404", "updated_at": "2013-01-22T23:40:05Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat", "login": "johndouthat", "gravatar_id": "13f37bc0645d1f6a473a61710ff205ce", "html_url": "https://github.com/johndouthat", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/13f37bc0645d1f6a473a61710ff205ce?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fdd61b41d5b91a9a09e504f025a87553b.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 40605, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/johndouthat/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-01-22T23:40:05Z", "id": 12573404, "owner": "rails"}
